data.description: New Price. The house is in the picturesque Timbercreek Estates, The home boasts solar panels and an EV charging station to help reduce energy costs and environmental impact. The two-story entryway with dual staircases makes for a grand and impressive first impression. The house includes a formal living room and dining room, The kitchen's breakfast area is open to the family room with fire place,  The master bedroom suite includes a sitting area that overlooks the pool and spa. The recently remodeled master bath adds a touch of modernity and comfort. On the first floor, which can serve as a bedroom or office. The second floor offers ample space for the family, including three bedrooms. Two of these bedrooms are connected by a Jack and Jill bathroom. The large game room comes with built-ins and an additional full bathroom. The backyard is designed for entertainment, featuring a pool, spa, and two patio areas.
